<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Production Enterprises at Standstill in Kostanay Oblast </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1506161194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Russian 0100 GMT 
15 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1506161194 </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty Kazakh Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [All figures as heard] </F>
  [Text] Due to 95 million tenge of debts for electricity, 
subunits of the ore mining giant Sokolovsko-Sarbayskiy 
production amalgamation came to a standstill. In its turn, the 
amalgamation has not been paid by the Karaganda metallurgical 
combine -- 160 million tenge, and the Magnitogorsk combine -- 24 
billion rubles. In Kostanay Oblast, for this or other reasons, 
enterprises such as the Dzhetygarinskiy asbestos combine, the 
Avtodiesel works, the largest textile company Kotex, and 
enterprises of the construction industry also came to a 
standstill. 

</TEXT>

