<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Deputy Defense Minister Killed in Ambush 15 Jun </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputy Defense Minister Killed in Ambush 15 Jun </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1506114394 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1100 GMT 
15 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1506114394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] INTERFAX has learned that Ramazan Rajabov, deputy 
defense minister of Tajikistan, was killed this morning in an 
ambush in Garmskiy Rayon. According to preliminary information, 
six guards were also killed. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

