<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   More on Killing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    More on Killing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1506170994 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 16 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> PM1506170994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Major Vasiliy Likholeta under general heading: </F>
"Shot from the Corner; Those Are the Tactics Resorted to 
Increasingly Frequently by Gunmen from Tajik Opposition"] 
  [Text]In the Last Hour 
  Major Vasiliy Likholeta, chief of the Tajikistan Defense 
Ministry press center, has reported to the editorial office that 
on 15 June at 0930 hours as they were traveling from the Khait 
population center, at crossroads near the hamlet of Nimich two 
vehicles carrying servicemen of the Tajikistan Defense Ministry 
were destroyed by automatic machine-gun fire from an ambush set 
up by gunmen. Six people were killed and one wounded man is in 
a serious state. The dead include Colonel R. Radzhabov, 
Tajikistan Deputy Defense Minister, and Captain S. Kholov, a 
directorate officer. An operation has started to block off and 
destroy the gang. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

