<F P=106> [Russian Federation President's Directive No. 280-rp] </F>
  [Text] With a view to completing the accommodation of the 
Russian Federation State Duma in the official residence 
determined by the Russian Federation president's 18 February 
1994 edict no. 334 "on the accommodation of the Russian 
Federation State Duma;" 
  1. The building at block 2, number 4, Vilgelm Pik Street, 
Moscow, shall be assigned as the place for the accommodation of 
the Moscow Federation of Trade Unions and the Moscow Oblast 
Council of Trade Unions. 
