<H3> <TI>   Ministry Estimates Hidden Unemployment at 2.5 Million </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministry Estimates Hidden Unemployment at 2.5 Million </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1606125094 Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY in Ukrainian 15 Jun 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> AU1606125094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev HOLOS UKRAYINY </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Unemployed on the Permission of </F>
Administration"] 
  [Text] At the beginning of June, 101,500 unemployed with 
the corresponding status were registered in Ukraine. This means 
that, over a five month period, their number has increased by 
18,500 persons, and Ukraine feels confident to be among those 
European countries, which enjoy the lowest level of unemployment. 
  At the same time, the Ministry of Statistics maintains that 
about 2.5 million actually jobless citizens do not have official 
status and are on leave of absence on the permission of the 
administration. 

</TEXT>

