<H3> <TI>   Explosion Reported at Logovaz Bank in Moscow </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Explosion Reported at Logovaz Bank in Moscow </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1606134194 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1200 GMT 16 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1606134194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Twenty minutes ago an explosion occurred in the 
building of the House of Actors in Staryy Arbat in Moscow. The 
premises of the Logovaz Bank were blown up. According to 
unconfirmed reports, there are casualities. Now our film crew 
is at the scene. You will see our reportage from the scene in 
the evening edition. 

