<DATE1>  17 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Uzbekistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Officials Discuss Surkhandarya Oblast's Shortcomings </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Officials Discuss Surkhandarya Oblast's Shortcomings </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1706103194 Tashkent Radio Tashkent Network in Uzbek 0215 
GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1706103194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tashkent Radio Tashkent Network </F>
<F P=105>  Uzbek </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A meeting was held in the Surkhandarya oblast 
mayor's office [hakimiyat] devoted to the results of the check 
carried out by the special commission for increasing the pace of 
reforms in agriculture and also supervision of the 
implementation of the president's decrees and the government's 
decisions on this question. It was chaired by Jurabekov, first 
deputy prime minister of the republic and chairman of this 
commission. 
  Reports by Nuraliyev, mayor [hakim] of the oblast and the 
mayors of the neighboring rayons were heard. Measures for 
quickly overcoming the serious shortcomings, discovered by the 
commission, which emerged during implementation of the reforms 
in agriculture, privatization, and providing farmers with 
all-round support were defined. 

</TEXT>

