<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "L. Kuchma Uses CIA Forecasts To </F>
Scare People"] 
  [Text] The U.S. Central Intelligence Agency predicts that 
Ukraine will disintegrate this year for both ethnic and economic 
reasons. This was stated by Ukrainian presidential candidate 
Leonid Kuchma at a meeting with Zaporizhzhya residents at the 
